Name:                concrete-typerep
Version:             0.1.0.1
x-revision: 1
Synopsis:            Binary and Hashable instances for TypeRep
Description:         Binary and Hashable instances for TypeRep
License:             BSD3
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Reiner Pope
Maintainer:          reiner.pope@gmail.com
Category:            Data
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-version:       >=1.9.2

flag new-typerep
  Description: Build with base >= 4.4.0
  Default: False

Library
  Exposed-modules:     Data.ConcreteTypeRep

  Build-depends:       binary, hashable

  if flag(new-typerep)
     Build-depends: base >= 4.4 && < 4.4, ghc >= 7.2
     cpp-options:   -DNEW_TYPEREP
  else
     Build-depends: base < 4.4

Test-Suite tests
  type: exitcode-stdio-1.0
  Main-is: Main.hs
  hs-source-dirs: tests
  build-depends: 
      base,
      binary,
      concrete-typerep,
      hashable,
      test-framework,
      test-framework-quickcheck2,
      QuickCheck >= 2.4
      
      
